        <h2><strong>Income Tax Slab Rates for FY 2017-18(AY 2018-19)</strong></h2>
<p class="m20">For FY 2017-18, the slab rate for income tax up to Rs. 5 lakh has gone down from 10% to 5%.</p>
<h3></h3>
<h3><strong>PART I:</strong> <strong>Income Tax Slab for Individual Tax Payers &amp; HUF (Less Than 60 Years Old) (Both Men &amp; Women)</strong></h3>
<table class="table table-header-striped table-bordered">
<colgroup>
<col width="130" />
<col width="80" />
