<p>If you are registered as a company, the income tax slab rates do not apply to you. Domestic companies are taxed at 30% on the total income. A 5% surcharge is payable if income is more than Rs 1 crore but less than Rs 10 crore. If total income is more than Rs 10 crore, 10% surcharge is applicable.</p>
<h3 id="current-year-tax-slab" class="m40 mb20"><strong>Some Incomes are Taxed at Special Rates</strong></h3>
